CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: International General Insurance Holdings Ltd is an international specialist commercial insurer and reinsurer, underwriting a diverse portfolio of specialty lines. The company operates in a portfolio of Energy, Property, Construction, Engineering, Ports and Terminal, Financial Institutions, General Aviation, Professional Indemnity, Casualty, Directors and Officers, Political Violence, Forestry, and Treaty Reinsurance. Its operating segment includes Specialty Longtail; Specialty Short tail and Reinsurance. The company generates maximum revenue in the United Kingdom.
